<p style="text-align: center">
<span class="PRTitle"><!-- NewsTitle.start -->Transcript of Interview after 6th hearing on Helicopter Scam<!-- NewsTitle.end --></span>
</p>
<!-- NewsBody.start -->

<p style="text-align: justify">STG:   Itong mga helicopters ay naging kasaysayan at kasangkapan ng panloloko sa taumbayan. Binili ang choppers para gamitin sa pandaraya sa 2004 presidential elections tapos ng presidential elections ay ginamit pang good time nila - pagpunta sa Malaca&ntilde;ang, pagpunta sa mga golf course sa Pampanga, during the time they were  in power. To add insult to injury, at the end of their term, binenta pa itong mga helicopters sa Philippine National Police as brand new. Alam naman natin lahat na second hand. Kasangkapan ito ng panloloko sa taumbayan.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">Q:        Na-establish ba yung second-hand choppers ay iyon ang ginamit ni Moner?</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">STG:   Hindi pa klaro lahat iyon sapagkat limang choppers iyon so hindi klaro kung alin doon sa lima o apat? One of the logs, the name of Judge Moner, does appear and it's signed by the pilot.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">Q:        Considering na nacover today yung sa election fraud, ite-terminate na ba ang investigation sa choppers?</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">STG:   There's a question whether this will be the last on the choppers, well there is enough already to make a committee report. This might be the last for now . Ayoko magsalita ng tapos sapagkat nag-aantay pa kami ng dokyumento pero mag-uumpisa na kami sa paggawa ng committee report. Ang nangyari today , ay nag branch out na to the election fraud. In the next hearing, we will concentrate on the election fraud already.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">Q:        Ang nangyari ay parang naging first day ng hearing on poll fraud?</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">STG:   Yes, parang naging first day today.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">Q:        Magtake over na ba ang committee ni Sen. Pimentel?</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">STG:   The election fraud is referred to the Blue Ribbon Committee but as you can see, Sen. Pimentel is very active on the election fraud investigation.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">Q:        Any additional cases that you will file?</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">STG:   We will study the matter and aside from the committee report, we will file the necessary cases.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">Q:        Wala pang decision ang Blue Ribbon kung anong kaso ang isasampa?</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">STG:   Wala pa.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">Q:        So it's between plunder and violation of anti-corruption?</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">STG:   Yes, we're studying that. Those are the options.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">Q:        On Moner.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">STG:   That makes it credible because it is a turn around and conscience testimony now. Secondly, being a Muslim, he swore with the Koran on hand. I take that as very serious sign on his part that he really means to tell the truth this time.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">Q:        Security matters of Moner.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">STG:   He has security from the senate.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">Q:        Ano ang hiningi niyang condition para magsalita siya dito?</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">STG:   Hindi condition. Humingi lang ng security. Hindi yung " bigyan niyo ako otherwise hindi ako pupunta".</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">Q:        Until when?</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">STG:   Until the whole process is over.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">Q:        When is the next hearing?</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">STG:   Most likely next week.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">Q:        Ipapatawag niyo ba si Cusi?</p>
<p style="text-align: justify">STG:   In the spirit of fair play , we should call him so that he can have a chance to give his side and all the others named.</p>

